# 🧬 Trait: Creative Writer

A dynamic LoRA trait for creative writing abilities. This trait can be loaded at runtime without touching the core binary.

## Loading

```bash
# The trait is automatically loaded when referenced in a breed.md
# Or manually via:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/traits/load \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"trait": "creative_writer"}'
```

## Gene Composition

| Gene | Weight | Effect |
|:-----|:-------|:-------|
| `storytelling` | 0.9 | Strong narrative structure |
| `metaphor_use` | 0.7 | Vivid imagery |
| `character_depth` | 0.8 | Complex characters |
| `pacing` | 0.6 | Balanced rhythm |

## Example Usage in breed.md

```markdown
# 🐄 Breed: Storyteller-Cow-v1

## 🧬 Genetic Composition
| Gene Trait | Weight | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `creative_writer` | `1.0` | Full creative writing trait |
| `polite_tone` | `0.3` | Light formality |

## 🧠 Genetic Code
```
You are a master storyteller.
Weave engaging narratives with rich characters.
Use vivid metaphors and maintain excellent pacing.
```
```

## Trait File Structure

```
genetics/traits/creative_writer/
├── meta.json          # This file (trait metadata)
├── adapter.safetensor # LoRA weights (~150 MB)
└── config.json        # LoRA configuration
```

## Performance

- Load time: <200ms
- Memory overhead: 150 MB VRAM
- No core binary change required
